.TH restless 1 "Restless CLI"
.SH NAME
restless \- API topology inference CLI

.SH SYNOPSIS
restless [command] [flags]

.SH DESCRIPTION
Restless discovers, models, inspects and explains API surfaces using bounded traversal and safe HTTP methods.

.SH COMMANDS
scan        perform endpoint discovery
map         print structural overview of endpoints
inspect     inspect an endpoint or method
graph       render API topology
learn       documentation-aware discovery
teach       explain inferred structure
copilot     suggest next exploration steps
version     print build metadata

.SH STATE
Session state is stored using the XDG state directory:

$XDG_STATE_HOME/restless/state.json

Fallback location:

~/.local/state/restless/state.json

Legacy compatibility path:

~/.restless_state.json

.SH NETWORK MODEL
Restless performs bounded discovery using safe HTTP methods only:

GET
HEAD
OPTIONS

Traversal is restricted to the original host.

.SH EXAMPLES
restless scan https://api.example.com
restless map
restless inspect GET /users
restless graph

.SH AUTHOR
Restless contributors
